fields.name: VENUM ARROW LOMA SIGNATURE COLLECTION JOGGERS - BLACK/WHITE
fields.description:

Soft and durable, they will allow you to combine style and comfort.

Thanks to their slim fit and detailed design, these sweatpants perfectly match a sporty look.

The cotton and elastane side bands give you a touch of style, the polyester / elastane mix ensure total comfort.





This model measures  190 cm, weighs 82 kg and wears a size M product. His chest measurement is 103 cm and his waist measurement is 83 cm.

fields.name: VENUM TROOPER BOMBER - KHAKI/BLACK
fields.description:
The Trooper bomber jacket is a light and comfortable jacket. Versatile, it complements both jeans and joggers. This jacket has two zipped side pockets as well as an internal pocket. This model measures  177 cm, weighs 80 kg and wears a size M product. His chest measurement is 96 cm and his waist measurement is 74 cm.

fields.name: VENUM GIANT HOODY - BLACK/WHITE
fields.description:
The Venum Giant hoodie is an ultra comfortable hooded jacket with a fitted cut. Its brushed interior is extremely soft and provides optimal thermal insulation.

This sweatshirt has two zipped side pockets. It is associated with the Venum Giant jogging pants for a 100% fightwear look!

fields.name: VENUM BANDIT SWEATSHIRT - BLACK/GREY
fields.description:
The Bandit collection speaks to the DNA of our brand: a cutting-edge and original design paying respect to the brand's origins.



The Bandit Jacket is the perfect example: its slim fitting cut and its urban sporty look makes it a must have for any fans of the brand. Comfortable and durable, it will go perfectly with jeans for a street ready look.



Venum purists might prefer the 100% fightwear look by wearing it with the Bandit joggers!





This model measures  180 cm, weighs 75 kg and wears a size M product. His chest measurement is 99 cm and his waist measurement is 78 cm.

fields.name: VENUM ORIGINS HOODIE LOMA EDITION BLUE/YELLOW
fields.description:
Designed not to go unnoticed, this Venum Origins sweatshirt from the “LOMA” signature collection has an ultra modern and sporty look, as well as a fitted cut.

The selected materials are suitable for training or use in the every day.

The Loma Origins jacket has an adjustable hood with drawstrings as well as waterproof zipped pockets on the left sleeve and on the chest, which allow you to keep your valuables safe, even in bad weather.

The Loma Origins jacket can be worn with the matching pants to complete the set.

fields.name: VENUM ART BOMBER - BLACK/WHITE €124.99
fields.description:
With military origins, the Venum Art bomber jacket is made of 100% Polyester both inside and the outer lining, guaranteeing you a light and practical jacket whatever the weather.

The Venum Art bomber jacket has three front zip pockets. It also includes a utility pocket on the sleeve.

The color of the Venum Art bomber jacket is highlighted by a bright red patterned inner lining that offers an ultra modern look.

The seams on the entire jacket have been reinforced for increased durability.

The Art bomber jacket also features a Venum logo on the chest.

This bomber jacket can be worn with jeans as well as with a jogging bottoms - your call.

fields.name: VENUM ARROW LOMA SIGNATURE COLLECTION HOODIE - DARK CAMO
fields.description:
The Venum Arrow Camo Sweatshirt is part of the outfit worn by champion Vasyl Lomachenko during the unification of the WBC, WBA, WBO titles at the O2 Arena in London.

Its sporty and urban design can accompany you during your daily activities, and can also be used during your training sessions.

This sweatshirt has a "fitted" cut.

The Loma touch is present thanks to the embroidered inscriptions on the hood and the presence of the Loma logo, detailed and with shimmering reflections.

fields.name: VENUM LASER EVO HOODIE - KHAKI CAMO
fields.description:
The EVO Laser Sweatshirt has a slim fit design to guarantee a clean and modern look.

Keeping you warm thanks to its perfect combination of cotton and polyester, offering excellent insulation and optimal body heat management.

This sweatshirt features an adjustable hood with rubber-tipped drawstrings and nylon inserts at the shoulders to ensure a perfect fit. Equipped with waterproof zipped pockets, small items will be kept safely at your fingertips and protected from the elements.

The Laser EVO sweatshirt will be a long-lasting addition to your wardrobe thanks to its reinforced seams, thermo-glued graphic design, and diagonally reinforced zipper.

fields.name: VENUM CONTENDER 2.0 BOXING GLOVES - WHITE/CAMO
fields.description:
The Contender 2.0 boxing gloves have been completely redesigned in comparison to the previous version. More durable, the Contender 2.0 boxing gloves also provide more protection than the 1.0 edition. The shock absorption is ensured by a high density injected foam while the attached thumb and the wide cuff guarantee the protection of the thumb and wrist. The shape of the glove has also been completely revised to provide a more secure and comfortable hand position.



Ideal for regular boxing, Muay Thai and kickboxing, these gloves are perfectly suited for moderate intensity training

fields.name: VENUM KONTACT EVO SHIN GUARDS - BLACK/RED
fields.description:
The Venum "Kontact Evo" shin guards have been engineered to flex and form naturally with the motion of your shin and your instep in order to provide the ultimate anatomical protection.
Their flexible hinge - with elastic straps - fits comfortably to anyone of your positions and leg shapes delivering a secure maintain during intense action and enhanced mobility. Contouring your leg the Venum "Kontact Evo" shin guards acts as a second strong layer of skin, making them ultra versatile and adapted to wide range of combat sports: MMA, Muay Thai, Kick Boxing, Karate, Taekwondo …
Benefiting from a low-profile construction, the Venum "Kontact Evo" shin guards are designed with reinforced foam strategically placed, from your instep to the top of your shin. Delivering an optimal shield of your striking surface, the Venum "Kontact Evo" shin guards ensure superior protection during attack or defense phases.
Open areas and mesh panels have been designed in order to facilitate the sweat escape and accelerate your body thermoregulation.
Featuring 3D embossed grip, the Venum "Kontact Evo" shin guards will help you to increase your takedown and sprawl techniques with unmatched mat traction. More stable, you will be able to deploy all your power with strong and dynamic kicks.

fields.name: VENUM PREDATOR MOUTHGUARD - BLACK/KHAKI
fields.description:
The Venum Predator Mouthguard provides a perfect combination of unbelievable comfort, flexibility, and shock absorption.

The perfect low profile design and advanced Nextfit Gel Frame that molds to your teeth is not only a perfect and comfortable custom fit, but also allows better breathability during training.

Its dual-core design made with a high density rubber frame, the Venum Predator Mouthguard aligns to your jaw, ensuring better absorption with every impact.
